summary:
EWIs Whiterun
******************
My personal Work that I would like to share now with the rest of the Community.
This Texture Set adding new Graphics with higher Resolution and great Details to the vanilla Game
and gives Whiterun a beautiful and unique look.
Not everyone's taste but i love it.

Features

[color=#ffff00]My personal Work that I would like to share now with the rest of the Community.
This Texture Set adding new Graphics with higher Resolution and great Details to the vanilla Game
and gives Whiterun a beautiful and unique look.
Not everyone's taste but i love it.[/color]

[color=#00ffff]Features:[/color]
[color=#ffff00]Resolution: 1k (parallax* map 512 kb). Doors 2k.
*My Mod requires ENB and Project Parallax Remastered by osmodius.

[/color][color=#ff0000]recommended:[/color] [color=#00ffff]JK's Whiterun[/color]
[color=#bf9000]******************[/color]
[color=#00ffff]Install:[/color]
[color=#ffff00]Using your favorite Mod Manager or extract to your Skyrim main folder.
enjoy.
ewi65[/color]
